---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jumbo Stainless Steel Wire Pegs"
  description="Our largest stainless steel wire peg — perfect for pillows, doonas, camping, and heavy items. Opens up to 20mm wide. Never breaks."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-4">Specialty · Jumbo</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-800 leading-tight mb-6">Jumbo Stainless Steel Wire Pegs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">Our biggest, strongest peg — for the jobs that regular pegs can't handle.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Product specs</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Grade</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">201 Stainless Steel</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Wire Diameter</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">2.3mm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Length</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">8.5cm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Opening Width</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Up to 20mm</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">When you need a bigger peg</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Our jumbo peg is 8.5cm long — nearly 50% larger than our standard peg — and opens up to almost 20mm wide. It's designed for gripping large, thick items that standard pegs struggle with.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Perfect for pillows, doonas, sleeping bags, camping gear, and heavy denim. Also brilliant for the garden and around the home for any job that needs a strong, large clip.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Made from one piece of wire — so like all Wire Pegs, it will never break, snap, or fall apart.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Best for</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Pillows and doonas</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Sleeping bags and camping gear</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Heavy jeans, towels and thick fabric</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Garden and home use as a large clip</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Anyone who needs extra holding power</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-stone-800 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-stone-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Jumbo Pegs at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products/windy-conditions" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">← Windy Conditions Pegs</a>
      <a href="/products/sock-hangers" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">View Sock Hangers →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>